      comments: []
    - name: '22: '
      title: 
      number: 22
      content: "\u201CAnd so, Oholibah, Lord <smallcaps>Yahweh</smallcaps> says to
        you: \u2018Behold, I will stir up all your former lovers against you, from
        whom you have withdrawn your affection. I will bring them against you from
