          possibly, \u201CThey will attack you equipped [for battle].\u201D     
          The Hebrew has different words for shields; two are found in this verse,
          one for large shields and one for small.    denotes a large shield like
          a \u201Cbody protector,\u201D while    denotes a smaller, round shield.    "
    - name: '25: '
      title: 
      number: 25
      content: 'I will direct my fiery indignation against you and let them treat
        you with fury. They will slice off your nose and ears, and what is left of
        your people will fall by the sword. They will capture your surviving sons
        and daughters and burn them alive. '
      comments: []
    - name: '26: '
      title: 
      number: 26
