      title: 
      number: 23-27
      content: "\u201CAs regards the remaining tribes south of this sacred section,
        each tribe is to receive one portion of land that extends from the eastern
        boundary west to the Mediterranean Sea:BenjaminSimeonIssacharZebulunGad."
